comments: Beasley (MIN) slightly extends his forearm into Gordon (DEN) during the drive but Gordon's momentum carries him away from the marginal contact.
Jokic (DEN) and Towns (MIN) mutually engage in marginal arm to arm contact prior to disengaging during the rebound.
Towns (MIN) makes contact to Jokic's (DEN) wrist that affects his jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) places two hands on Jokic (DEN) and the contact marginal.
Edwards (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Gordon (DEN) lightly brushes Edwards' (MIN) arm and the marginal contact does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) makes marginal contact to Morris' (DEN) body during the drive that does not affect his SBQR.
Russell (MIN) briefly grasps Morris' (DEN) jersey during his dribble and Russell immediately removes his hand. The contact is marginal.
Russell (MIN) reaches in and makes contact to Morris' (DEN) arm that affects his SQBR during the pass attempt.
Towns (MIN) and Jokic (DEN) briefly engage in marginal body contact during the drive. After absorbing the body contact, Towns swipes down and makes contact with the ball.
Barton (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position and makes contact with the ball during Beasley's (MIN) shot attempt near the rim.
There is no angle that conclusively shows Barton (DEN) make contact with the ball while he is out of bounds.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during Edwards' (MIN) shot attempt near the rim.
Barton (DEN) steps inbounds with his right foot and lifts his left from the baseline before making contact with the ball.
